* Mathematical writing
  Some of my mathematical writings are uploaded to sharelatex. *org-mode* support for LaTeX is in
 my oppinion even better than Wordpress and I am not bluffing, this $\nabla_{\dot\gamma}\dot\gamma =
 0$ is one, and here is another

\[ \int_0^\infty e^{-x^2}dx = \frac{\sqrt{\pi}}{2} \]

Mathematics however (at least mine) are
  not just about what you write between the $-signs, mathematics are also about structures, things
  you put between

  \begin{lemma}, \end{theorem}, \ref{lem}, ...

  There seems to be no easy and reusable method for this (that is more efficient than emacs +
  auctex + reftex + yasnippet) and that is why I will put almost everything in sharelatex. Here they
  are



